						<summary>

						<p>Chōḻa, Parakēsarivarman [mistake for Rājakēsarivarman] Kulōttuṅga II, 20th year, Kanyā, sudi 11, Thursday, Śravaṇa = A.D. 1152, September 11.</p>						

						<p>Gift of 100 sheep for a lamp by Araiyan Tannaṉ Edirilāppēraraiyaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kulōttuṅgachōḻa-kaḍambarāyaṉ of Chār in Uṟattūr-kūṟṟam.</p>						

