<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> kOpparakEcari pa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rāṉa tiripuvaṉaccakkara
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulōttuṅ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>cōḻa tēvaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="20">2 <g type="numeral">10</g></num>
<lb n="5"/>Iraṭṭapāṭi koṇṭa cōḻa vaḷanā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭṭu Uṟattūrk kūṟṟattu vaṭakō
<lb n="7" break="no"/>nāṭṭu Uṭaiyār tirupperumā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṉāṇṭāṟku Innāṭṭu cāra
<lb n="9" break="no"/>raiyan tannaṉ Etirilāppe
<lb n="10" break="no"/>raiyanāṉa kulōttuṅka cō
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḻak kaṭamparāyaṉ Ivvā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṭṭaik kaṉināyaṟṟup pū<hi rend="grantha">rva</hi>
<lb n="13"/>pa<hi rend="grantha">kṣa</hi>ttu Ēkā<hi rend="grantha">daśi</hi>yum viyāḻa
<lb n="14"/>kiḻamaiyum peṟṟa tiruvōṇattu
<lb n="15"/>nāḷ vaitta tirunantāviḷakku
<lb n="16"/>Ivviḷakku Onṟum viṭṭu 
