<lb n="18"/>civappirāmaṇarōm kaikko
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ṇṭu Ivviḷakku Onṟum nāṅka
<lb n="20" break="no"/>ḷ cantirātittavarai Eri<unclear>kkak</unclear> kaṭavōmāka
<lb n="21" break="no"/>upaiyam koṇṭōm Ikkōyi
<lb n="22" break="no"/>l civappirāmaṇarrōm §
